4. Release and execution boundary

AISRAF v0.1.2 is limited to AM3 / AL3 local orchestrated runtime evidence and
an AL2 controlled-output local workbench. There is no AM4 adapter execution.
There is no Jira, Confluence, Lucidchart, Rovo/MCP, cloud, database,
Terraform, event bus, telemetry, or external post-back execution in v0.1.2.
AL5 closed-loop autonomy is out of scope.

